data.description: SPACIOUS 5 BEDROOM/3.5 BATH MODERN CRAFTSMAN ON CUL-DE-SAC IN SOUGHT AFTER STILLWOOD FARMS! This home will impress you from the moment you enter the two-story foyer. Features Include: Open Concept Floor Plan, Primary Bedroom on Main Level, Generous Secondary Bedrooms, Formal Dining Room with Crown Molding and Wainscoting, Fresh Paint, New Carpet, Gleaming Laminate Flooring, Dine-in Chef's Kitchen with Granite Countertops, Custom Backsplash, Breakfast Bar, Breakfast Nook, Wood Cabinetry and Stainless Steel Appliances. The sun-drenched living room is adjacent to the kitchen and boasts a stacked stone fireplace and direct access to the expansive rear deck. The oversized primary retreat offers tray ceilings, a large walk-in closet and en suite bath with double vanities, granite countertops, water closet, soaking tub and a separate shower. Completing the main level is a laundry room and a thoughtfully placed powder room. Upstairs, you'll find three ample bedrooms, a full bath and a loft/media room. The terrace level boasts a guest suite, full bath, family/bonus room, home office and tons of storage. Stepping outside, the backyard presents a harmonious blend of a patio, deck and green space, allowing you to enjoy the outdoors and the privacy of the conservation easement the borders the property. With a two-car garage, parking and storage needs are well accommodated. Community amenities include swimming, clubhouse, playground and a park. Conveniently located near shopping, dining and I85! Click the Virtual Tour link to experience the 3D Walkthrough today!
